        <field>Remediation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Remove Create permission from the guest profile on Case and Lead. Use Salesforce Web-to-Case or Web-to-Lead features with CAPTCHA protection as a secure alternative for public form submissions.</value>
